Feel free to compile and run and distribute any code.
(http://www.github.com/joshmg)

README Last Updated: November 10, 2010

All libraries compiled and linked with with MSVS 2010 "Microsoft (R) 32-bit C/C++ Optimizing Compiler Version 16.00.30319.01 for 80x86".

This code has only been tested on a Windows environment.

There is a known bugs that occurs when merging models that results in irrecoverable color data loss. This is thought to originate from from editing-model to model3d object translation.
